{"id": "ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 12, "displayName": {"text": "Sweet Please", "languageCode": "zh"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuemVTdWpRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I've finally found my go-to cake shop! Sweet Please is absolutely amazing. They constantly refresh their menu with new and exciting creations, so there's always something tempting to try.  But the best part is that they use incredibly fresh, high-quality ingredients.\n\nThe first time I tried their pistachio and cherry, I was blown away. It was seriously one of the best cakes I've ever had.  I raved about it to all my friends, and now they're hooked too!\n\nAnd I have to mention how wonderful the owner is! She's so incredibly nice and accommodating.  She even offered curbside delivery and packed my cake perfectly with an ice bag when she knew I was taking it on a road trip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I've finally found my go-to cake shop! Sweet Please is absolutely amazing. They constantly refresh their menu with new and exciting creations, so there's always something tempting to try.  But the best part is that they use incredibly fresh, high-quality ingredients.\n\nThe first time I tried their pistachio and cherry, I was blown away. It was seriously one of the best cakes I've ever had.  I raved about it to all my friends, and now they're hooked too!\n\nAnd I have to mention how wonderful the owner is! She's so incredibly nice and accommodating.  She even offered curbside delivery and packed my cake perfectly with an ice bag when she knew I was taking it on a road trip.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Menglan Wu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106586236133068161914/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzNmtnahDEyq2nf6TrhgnCjIxnVNBVyo_haJSYDqBvayhWflOQJg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-08T14:51:58.939402Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuemVTdWpRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURuemVTdWpRRRAB!2m1!1s0x808fcdeceeddb48b:0xf519faa01db9d97a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPZUp6czZBN2VYSUlREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It's a little cake kitchen but the taste and look of their bakeries and cakes are just amazing!! I've ordered over five time's and the cakes never disappoint me! Finally find my go to place at bay area, they are the best! Attaching a photo of mother's day's special! That's amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It's a little cake kitchen but the taste and look of their bakeries and cakes are just amazing!! I've ordered over five time's and the cakes never disappoint me! Finally find my go to place at bay area, they are the best! Attaching a photo of mother's day's special! That's amazing.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Minghao Yang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105731359409834287630/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc7Lz0a7tQbc5lJ9k3atPTMIiEVcRu4aXzu0rA_Oiqx7GKdxvoOQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-05-12T02:20:39.925249Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPZUp6czZBN2VYSUlREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VPZUp6czZBN2VYSUlREAE!2m1!1s0x808fcdeceeddb48b:0xf519faa01db9d97a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNiM0pfUlV3EAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My husband got me a box of mini cakes for my birthday.  They are both beautiful & delicious!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My husband got me a box of mini cakes for my birthday.  They are both beautiful & delicious!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "jennifer fioretti", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109794431805071421464/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQy0bH18brp2u8fyramD3o9eolTuCTvnbxbXUnP9oLYPd2mfP4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2024-07-24T15:15:36.747705Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNiM0pfUlV3EAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNiM0pfUlV3EAE!2m1!1s0x808fcdeceeddb48b:0xf519faa01db9d97a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURqa2Y2UHl3RRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Love it! This spring cake set is really delicate and tastes so good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love it! This spring cake set is really delicate and tastes so good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CC Cai", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107220329308491332266/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU3TxtiHnZCDxLP3G0E__-_C5hvso71K75St4KrYbFFYqPVg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2024-05-04T08:27:09.223466Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURqa2Y2UHl3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURqa2Y2UHl3RRAB!2m1!1s0x808fcdeceeddb48b:0xf519faa01db9d97a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7Td7uzNj4ARetm5HaD6GfU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paUVIxSXdRVFp6WWpsblVrWkJURE53VVZVNVVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text